Jigsaw Puzzle v1.2 Shareware. 
DOS 3.1, EGA or VGA, 500K RAM.
The first truly realistic jigsaw 
puzzle simulation features original 
artwork, piece grouping, and three 
levels of difficulty. Mouse or 
keyboard operation. Recommended 
for ages 3 to 93. Runs well on 
286 and low memory PCs.


 
